NAME
    RT-Extension-NKSC - RT and RTIR modifications for NKSC


RT VERSION
    Works with RT > 4.2.0

INSTALLATION
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install
        May need root permissions

    Edit your /opt/rt4/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm
        Add this line:

            Plugin('RT::Extension::NKSC');

    Clear your mason cache
            rm -rf /opt/rt4/var/mason_data/obj

    Restart your webserver
